<p>
<note n="0549001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0549001">（便宜上表題ヲ附ス。<g ref="#CB18834">󴦒</g>）</note>
<note n="0549002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0549002">（【標】ハ旧版ニオケル冠註ヲ示ス。<g ref="#CB18834">󴦒</g>）</note>
<note n="0549003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0549003">目錄新作</note>
<note n="0549b01" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0549b01">始終由于淨國故以佛國冠于篇首</note>
<note n="0549b02" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0549b02">如是信順辭也信則理順理順則道成經無豐約非信不傳故建言如是</note>
<note n="0549b03" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0549b03">曰我聞則不執于我而諍競無由生矣</note>
<note n="0549b04" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0549b04">修行工夫大約有四曰靜曰定曰慧曰通一步進一步一層深一層見境不著見阻不退謹謹護持自然成就</note>
<note n="0549b05" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0549b05">盖諸大眾者明其超出蓋大眾也</note>
<note n="0550b01" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0550b01">虗空藏菩薩手執四珠遍照空界與金剛明經四如來混合一室者正發明是義</note>
<note n="0550b02" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0550b02">既得法身入無為境心不可智求形不可像取故曰無量</note>
<note n="0550b03" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0550b03">法身無生而無不生無生故惡趣門閉無不生故現身五道</note>
<note n="0550b04" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0550b04">功不可虗設故不唐捐</note>
<note n="0550b05" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0550b05">本菩提心為海導師固宜諸菩薩歡欣會坐而聽法也</note>
<note n="0550b06" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0550b06">尸棄梵王名秦言頂髻也</note>
<note n="0550b07" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0550b07">收結一喻奇古之甚</note>
<note n="0550b08" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0550b08">蓋以不廣而彌八極土亦不狹而現蓋中阿羅漢見閻君（君疑浮）提如觀掌中果諸菩薩等見百千界十方如來窮盡微塵清淨國土無所不囑眾生洞視不過方寸</note>
<note n="0550b09" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0550b09">淨名之鉢屬厭萬口寶積之蓋徧覆十方若知法界本造于心則知凡夫皆具此理</note>
<note n="0550b10" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0550b10">天竺有青蓮華其葉修而廣青白分明目亦如之</note>
<note n="0550b11" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0550b11">俗王以俗力勝民故澤及一國法王以法力超眾故道濟無疆</note>
<note n="0550b12" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0550b12">法從緣生誰主宰之故無我既無我誰造善惡誰受禍福耶故云云</note>
<note n="0550b13" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0550b13">法輪常淨猶虗空也時移俗易而聖聖相傳</note>
<note n="0550b14" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0550b14">老病死重患也濟以法藥故為大醫王</note>
<note n="0551b01" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0551b01">自欣所獻小而覩變大也</note>
<note n="0551b02" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0551b02">十力備故即以為名</note>
<note n="0551b03" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0551b03">三界尊覩蓋中之瑞也</note>
<note n="0551b04" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0551b04">不共者不與二乘共也</note>
<note n="0551b05" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0551b05">密口一音殊類異解</note>
<note n="0551b06" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0551b06">一音演而歡畏異豈二乘所共耶</note>
<note n="0551b07" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0551b07">我染諸法故諸法縛我無染則縛解矣</note>
<note n="0551b08" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0551b08">聖心無寄猶無依</note>
<note n="0551b09" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0551b09">阿耨多羅無上也三藐三菩提正徧知也菩提解在後</note>
<note n="0551b10" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0551b10">土所以淨豈矯飾所能淨之必由于行故請說行也</note>
<note n="0551b11" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0551b11">此下釋眾生即佛土也佛土者即眾生之影響耳形脩則影長形短則影促豈日月使之然乎形自然耳故隨所化眾生之多少而取佛土之廣狹也</note>
<note n="0551b12" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0551b12">不諂直心一行異名也</note>
<note n="0551b13" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0551b13">外捨國財身命內捨貪愛慳嫉名一切能捨</note>
<note n="0551b14" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0551b14">得正智慧決定法相正定聚也四心周修無際故無量</note>
<note n="0551b15" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0551b15">以四等法攝眾生一曰財法施隨彼所須二曰以愛心和言隨彼所適三利行隨彼所利方便利之四曰同事遇惡同惡而斷其惡遇善同善而進其善</note>
<note n="0551b16" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0551b16">迴彼雜行向於一乘此迴向心也</note>
<note n="0551b17" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0551b17">犯禁譏彼不自守也</note>
<note n="0551b18" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0551b18">此言行因心而成蓋始于直心終于淨土也</note>
<note n="0551b19" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0551b19">捲簾法收盡上文極緊嚴勻淨無意為文文之最上乘也</note>
<note n="0552b01" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0552b01">始之直心終之功德見進為有漸不可一蹴至也</note>
<note n="0552b02" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0552b02">萬事萬形皆由心成各以所見而為證</note>
<note n="0552b03" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0552b03">顯淨土於未聞見猶開聾瞽于形聲也</note>
<note n="0552b04" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0552b04">無生法忍佛國之興其正為此法忍即慧性耳見法無生心智寂滅堪受不退故名</note>
<note n="0552b05" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0552b05">道非獨覺要師而後成故名聲聞乘</note>
</p>
